name: OfficeJet Pro 8125e All-in-One Printer
description: The HP OfficeJet Pro 8125e is a professional-grade color inkjet AIO designed for home office and small business environments. It offers the convenience of high-speed prints—up to 20 ppm black and 10 ppm color ISO—and premium print quality with up to 4800 × 1200 dpi optimized resolution. With features like automatic duplex printing, a 35-sheet ADF, a 2.7″ touchscreen, and HP+ smart functionality (including 3 months of Instant Ink and enhanced security), it's designed to be reliable, efficient, and eco-friendly—made of over 45% recycled plastic.

name: HP 67XL High Yield Black Original Ink Cartridge, 3YM57AN#140
description: he HP 67XL High Yield Black Original Ink Cartridge (3YM57AN#140) is designed to deliver high-quality, reliable printing for everyday use. As a high-yield version of the standard HP 67 cartridge, it offers a significantly greater page yield—up to approximately 240 pages—making it a more cost-effective option for frequent printing. It uses pigment-based black ink that produces sharp, crisp text and consistent results across various paper types. The cartridge is easy to install and works seamlessly with a wide range of HP DeskJet and ENVY series printers, ensuring smooth performance and minimal downtime. Additionally, it supports HP’s Smart features, such as ink level alerts and easy reordering through the HP Smart app. Environmentally conscious users will appreciate that it is made with up to 88% recycled plastic and is eligible for free recycling through the HP Planet Partners program.

name: HP 63XL High Yield Black Original Ink Cartridge, F6U64AN#140
description: The HP 63XL High Yield Black Original Ink Cartridge delivers up to twice the pages compared to the standard HP 63 cartridge, making it a reliable and cost-effective choice for frequent printing. It uses high-quality pigment-based ink that produces sharp, crisp text and professional-looking documents. Ideal for home or small office use, this cartridge is easy to install and ensures consistent performance across a wide range of compatible HP printers. Print more and replace less with this high-yield cartridge designed for efficiency and dependability.
